Things My mother taught me:\
My mother taught me to appreciate  job well cone \'96 \'93IF you\'92re going to kill each other do it outside, I just finished cleaning the house.\'94\
My mother taught me to religion \'96 You better pray that will come out of the carpet\
My mother taught me logic \'96 Because I said so that\'92s why\
My mother taught me IRONY \'96 Keep crying and I\'92ll give you something to cry about\
My mother taught me about the science of Osmosis \'96 Shut your mouth and eat your super.\
My mother taught me about Stamina \'96 You\'92ll sit there until all that spinach is gone.\
